{
  "name": "Seal Resistant",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/ring-circle-smoke-blue.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Chakra </p><p>Prerequisite: Proficiency in Chakra Control, Level 8+ </p><p>Your chakra is resilient to the effects of most sealing attempts.</p><p> You gain the following benefits: </p><p>• Increase your Constitution or Charisma score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• You gain a +2 bonus to Charisma saving throws vs jutsu with the Fuinjutsu keyword.</p><p>• You make checks to remove the Sealed condition at advantage.</p><p>• If a jutsu, effect, feature or trait would attempt to remove your ability to mold chakra without a saving throw, you instead make a constitution saving throw vs the jutsu types save DC.</p><p> If the effect was not cause by a jutsu, you instead make a DC 20 constitution saving throw, retaining your ability to mold chakra on a successful save.</p><p></p>",
